FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773194861
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FAnnouncing her decision to ban the
OL,7,Fmarch, Shabana Mahmood said she was
OL,8,F"satisfied doing so is necessary to
OL,9,Fprevent serious public disorder, due
OL,10,Fto the scale of the protest and
OL,11,Fmultiple counter-protests, in the
OL,12,Fcontext of the ongoing conflict in the
OL,13,FMiddle East".
OL,15,FShe added: "Should a stationary
OL,16,Fdemonstration proceed, the police will
OL,17,Fbe able to apply strict conditions.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@LO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773194861
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,F"I expect to see the full force of the
OL,7,Flaw applied to anyone spreading hatred
OL,8,Fand division instead of exercising
OL,9,Ftheir right to peaceful protest."
OL,11,FThe Islamic Human Rights Commission
OL,12,F(IHRC), which organises the protest,
OL,13,Fhas previously insisted the
OL,14,Fdemonstration is always "good natured
OL,15,Fand peaceful".
OL,17,FIt is the first time a protest march
OL,18,Fhas been banned since 2012.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]vD@YOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
