PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773194862
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FA spokesman for the IHRC, Faisal Bodi,
OL,7,Ftold the BBC's The World Tonight that
OL,8,Fit was "a sad day for freedom of
OL,9,Fexpression, freedom of assembly and
OL,10,Fthe right of people to legitimately
OL,11,Fprotest about issues they feel
OL,12,Fstrongly about".
OL,14,FHe added: "This demonstration has
OL,15,Ftaken place for the last 40 years
OL,16,Fpeacefully."
OL,18,FThe IHRC has previously expressed
OL,19,Fsupport for Iran's former supreme
OL,20,Fleader, the Ayatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,26,@pD@HOUtD@OO]vD@KOUxD@LO]
