PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773194862
OL,3,CHome Secretary grants police request
OL,4,Cto ban Al Quds Day march
OL,6,FFollowing his death in a US-Israeli
OL,7,Fairstrike last month, the group said
OL,8,FMr Khamenei "chose to stand on the
OL,9,Fright side of history" and described
OL,10,Fhim as "a rare role model" who would
OL,11,Fbe "mourned by freedom loving people
OL,12,Fall over the world".
OL,14,FThe Campaign Against Antisemitism
OL,15,Fwelcomed the decision to ban the
OL,16,Fmarch, saying it was "a positive
OL,17,Fdevelopment" and adding: "Allowing
OL,18,Fthis hate-fest to go ahead would have
OL,19,Fsent the message that Islamists rule
OL,20,Fthe roost in Britain."
